<item>
            <title>[SOLR-16619] `solr status` and `solr create` do not work on IBM i</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16619</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The `solr status` and `solr create` commands fail on the IBM i platform. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example&lt;br/&gt;
```&lt;br/&gt;
Solr process 3391 from /solr/solr-8.11.2/bin/solr-8983.pid not found&lt;br/&gt;
```&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Pase on IBM i using Java 11 with OpenJDK&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
